## Task Summary: Centralize clippy lint policy

**Track:** clippy-zero-warnings-2026-03-11
**Task:** Centralize duplicated #![deny(...)] blocks into [workspace.lints] and add clippy.toml
**Date:** 2026-03-11

### Changes

- Cargo.toml: added [workspace.lints.rust] and [workspace.lints.clippy] sections
- apps/cli/Cargo.toml, libs/*/Cargo.toml: added [lints] workspace = true
- apps/cli/src/main.rs, libs/*/src/lib.rs: removed duplicated #![deny(...)] blocks
- vendor/conch-parser/src/lib.rs: added #![allow(warnings)] to suppress vendored crate noise
- clippy.toml: new file with msrv=1.85 and threshold defaults

### Why

Lint configuration was duplicated across 4 crate roots with identical #![deny(...)] blocks.
Centralizing into [workspace.lints] makes the policy single-sourced and easier to maintain.
Vendored conch-parser (Rust 2015 edition) emitted 198 warnings that obscured real issues.
